'''21世紀百大電影'''（{{lang-en|100 Greatest Films of the 21st Century}}）是由[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]於2016年8月匯編的列表，由全球177位影評人的投票調查所選出<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cabin|first1=Chris|title=BBC Releases Its List of the 100 Best Movies of the 21st Century|url=https://collider.com/bbc-best-movies-21st-century-list/|website=Collider|date=2016-08-23|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803095205/https://collider.com/bbc-best-movies-21st-century-list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影評人根據自2000年以來所發行的最佳電影中提交前10部並匯集整理出該列表<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lawson|first1=Richard|title=Are These the 100 Best Movies of the 21st Century?|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/08/bbc-best-movies-2000s-list|website=Vanity Fair|date=2016-08-23|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2017-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170715180454/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/08/bbc-best-movies-2000s-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

